Folds

Author:
Little Girl

About:
This WoaS mod creates five help pages.

Content:
This mod creates these eight pages:

WoaS Mods::Add a logo to the banner
WoaS Mods::Add folds
WoaS Mods::Add footnotes
WoaS Mods::Add styled notes
WoaS Mods::Add styled nowiki text
WoaS Mods::Add tooltips
WoaS Mods::Add topnotes
WoaS Mods::Replace fixed menu area and topbar option

Instructions:
1) Extract the contents of this zip file to a directory on your computer.
2) Open your wiki in a browser.
3) Click the Advanced (tools) icon in the banner.
4) Click the Special::ImportWSIF link in the Maintenance section on the page.
5) Click the Browse... button to select a .wsif file in the directory you extracted this zip file into.
6) Click the Import WSIF button to import the file into your wiki.
7) Repeat step 5 and step 6 for each of the .wsif files in this mod.
8) Click the Advanced (tools) icon in the banner.
9) Click the Special::All Pages link in the Pages section.
10) Click the pages in the Woas Mods:: namespace for instructions on how to make various modifications to your wiki.
